p: Of the Third Judicial District of Washington Territory, holding Terms at Seattle, for the County of King.
The People of the United States of America, to the Sheriff of King Jefferson County Greeting:

We command you, that you have the bodys of Ed Olson Harry Simpson William Totterman William Darrin John Dohn Frank Kaf Thomas Stuart & G Fitz Gerald by you imprisoned and detained as it is said, together with the time and cause of such imprisonment and detention, by whatsoever name said
